info.brief_description: Bringing back an old story I thought I couldn't keep.
info.description:
A strange building has odd effects on people who use it.
Inspired by The Cabin, by DJ Noah, which I'd recommend.
Some rules first.
1: No drugs.
2: No killing off characters.
3: Pregnancy can be used to a point.
4: No insulting religions.
5: More than one person can be effected by said building.
6: Girls will be used mostly, though guys can, if you can find ways to fit them in.
7: Certain books or films and shows, Science Fiction for example won't be use. Same for Anime and celebrities.
info.pretty_title: The Return of Playing With Toys
